org.jhove2.app.util.documenter.displayer
Class FormatModuleTabDelimDisplayer

java.lang.Object
  org.jhove2.app.util.documenter.displayer.FormatModuleTabDelimDisplayer
All Implemented Interfaces:
DocumentationDisplayer
public class FormatModuleTabDelimDisplayer
extends Object
implements DocumentationDisplayer

Create a set of tab-delimited files for import into the Module Documentation Word Template For the identification section, the following files are created (depending on values in the Spring beans for the module, format, and profiles being documented) (with Format, ProfileFormat, Module, and Profile id info (Section 2: Identification) ModuleName_Id.txt For the Reference section (Section 3, the following file is ModuleName_Ref.txt For the reportable properties section (7), the following file is created, based on static analysis of the Module class being documented (i.e. traverse the reportable type, not the values of the Spring bean) ModuleName_Reportable_properties.txt

Author:
smorrissey
